<<<FORMATTING-OFF>>>
 As Bosco/Reggio (comm. to these verses) explain, 'In medieval
<<<FORMATTING-ON>>>
lapidaries the emerald symbolized, in addition to chastity, justice.
Further, in a passage of Brunetto Latini's ^Tresor~ (III.xiii.16),
